title: Cardinal Burns S02-E03 (Comedy)
description:
Cardinal Burns is a British television sketch show starring Seb Cardinal and Dustin Demri-Burns, shown on E4. The first series began on 8 May 2012.

This is the first 2 episodes of season 2. This version is better than the first episode I uploaded a while back; looks like no-one else is going to up these episodes, so I may as well get them out.
